title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 29 2022
description:
AOC and Elizabeth Warren want to open abortion clinics on red state federal lands. Buck says, "At the base of Pickett's Charge, you suddenly have an abortion clinic? This is next-level crazy." Joy Behar, continuing her run as C&B-dubbed dumbest TV commentator, thinks SCOTUS decision on praying football coach could apply to Colin Kaepernick. AOC: Biden should expand SCOTUS, end filibuster, because court took away rights of "pregnant people." A 29-year-old transgender man beats girls in teenage skateboarding contest. At what date will we be safe from Biden being able to pass any more bad bills this year?
